&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SAFEGUARDING CHILDREN ADVISOR&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Safeguarding &amp; Service Effectiveness &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Band 7&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;30 hours per week (0.8 wte)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Permanent &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Welcome to Your Healthcare CIC, we are a not for profit social enterprise, proud of delivering patient-led, high quality health and social care community services for residents in the Borough of Kingston, as part of the NHS family.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Your Healthcare is located in the South West of London within the Royal Borough of Kingston. Working as a Community Interest Company (CIC), our status allows us to invest any surplus or profit back into front line services, where it is needed most by you, our community.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Your Healthcare CIC is looking to recruit an experienced nurse as their Safeguarding children advisor. Based at Hollyfield House in Surbiton and with the flexibility to work from home, the successful candidate will provide expert advice and guidance to Your Healthcare staff as a part of the team of safeguarding professionals. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The post holder will work as part of a well-established integrated team and is required to have knowledge and experience of child protection and safeguarding procedures. You will work with the named nurse for safeguarding children to ensure supervision; training and safeguarding support is delivered to all our staff. You will be joining a safeguarding team, with well-established practice systems and processes. &lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; You will possess excellent communication skills with a passion for the delivery of high-quality care to safeguard the children and young people living in Kingston. In return we offer a supportive environment, working with an excellent team of committed professionals. Your will receive training for your role and supervision by the named nurse. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Your Healthcare is located in the South West of London within the Royal Borough of Kingston. Working as a Community Interest Company (CIC), our status allows us to invest any surplus or profit back into front line services, where it is needed most by you, our community.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;If you would like to contact us to discuss any aspects of this role please contact: Suzanne Cardillo-Zallo, Named Nurse Safeguarding children, 07585103156 suzanne.cardillo-zallo@yourhealthcare.org&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CLOSING DATE: 22nd November 2020&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;INTERVIEWS: 1st December 2020&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
